Package menufact.singleton

Class Menu

java.lang.Object
menufact.singleton.Menu
public class Menu extends Object
The Menu class represents a menu in a restaurant. It holds a collection of dishes, which are represented by PlatAuMenu objects, and allows the user to navigate through the menu and retrieve recipes associated with the dishes.
